12 A BILL
13 TO BE ENTITLED
14 AN ACT
15
16 To make supplemental appropriations for the fiscal year
17 ending September 30, 2026, from the Opioid Treatment and
18 Abatement Fund to the entities and for the purposes herein in
19 the amount of $43,138,650.
20 BE IT ENACTED BY THE LEGISLATURE OF ALABAMA:
21 Section 1. There is hereby appropriated from the Opioid
22 Treatment and Abatement Fund the sum of $43,138,650 for the
23 fiscal year ending September 30, 2026, to the entities and for
24 the purposes specified herein:
25 (1) To the Board of Pardons and Paroles for additional
26 recovery and facility services at CARE in Thomasville and PREP
27 facility modifications, $1,500,000.
28 (2) To the Department of Mental Health, $26,360,000. Of
